To truly access
our full capacity

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:26.920 align:middle line:10%
requires that we retrain and
rewire our nervous system

00:00:26.920 --> 00:00:29.590 align:middle line:10%
for more optimal functioning.

00:00:29.590 --> 00:00:33.310 align:middle line:84%
To get a better feel for this,
let's use a computer analogy.

00:00:33.310 --> 00:00:36.550 align:middle line:84%
Imagine for a moment that
the hardware of a computer

00:00:36.550 --> 00:00:38.060 align:middle line:90%
is like the body.

00:00:38.060 --> 00:00:41.980 align:middle line:84%
Its circuitry and wiring are
akin to the nervous system.

00:00:41.980 --> 00:00:45.610 align:middle line:84%
Its main processing
chip is like our brain.

00:00:45.610 --> 00:00:49.900 align:middle line:84%
And now imagine that the
operating system and software,

00:00:49.900 --> 00:00:52.390 align:middle line:84%
with all its application
and data files,

00:00:52.390 --> 00:00:56.800 align:middle line:84%
is equivalent to our
individual mind and soul.

00:00:56.800 --> 00:01:01.090 align:middle line:84%
Meanwhile, the user is our
spirit or higher intelligence,

00:01:01.090 --> 00:01:05.230 align:middle line:84%
which is connected to
the mind of the all.

00:01:05.230 --> 00:01:07.300 align:middle line:84%
In other words,
our mind and soul

00:01:07.300 --> 00:01:11.440 align:middle line:84%
function as the interface
or mediator between the body

00:01:11.440 --> 00:01:13.360 align:middle line:90%
and the spirit.

00:01:13.360 --> 00:01:15.070 align:middle line:90%
If our software, a.k.a.

00:01:15.070 --> 00:01:18.460 align:middle line:84%
our mind, has bugs or
faulty programming,

00:01:18.460 --> 00:01:21.920 align:middle line:84%
then we're going
to have problems.

00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:24.620 align:middle line:84%
This means that our
goal is twofold.

00:01:24.620 --> 00:01:29.770 align:middle line:10%
First, to debug the programming
of the mind, and second,

00:01:29.770 --> 00:01:34.870 align:middle line:10%
to optimize the circuitry of the
brain and neurological system.

00:01:34.870 --> 00:01:38.980 align:middle line:84%
Only then will we be able to
expand our conscious awareness

00:01:38.980 --> 00:01:41.620 align:middle line:90%
of who and what we truly are.

00:01:41.620 --> 00:01:45.070 align:middle line:84%
As spiritual beings
having a physical life,

00:01:45.070 --> 00:01:46.750 align:middle line:84%
rather than thinking
of ourselves

00:01:46.750 --> 00:01:51.020 align:middle line:84%
as physical beings first who
are now on a spiritual journey.

00:01:51.020 --> 00:01:56.350 align:middle line:84%
Let's remember that we are
spirit first and foremost.

00:01:56.350 --> 00:02:01.470 align:middle line:84%
And we are here to live a
fully awakened physical life.

00:02:01.470 --> 00:02:04.380 align:middle line:84%
In this episode, we
begin diving into how

00:02:04.380 --> 00:02:08.000 align:middle line:84%
we can rewire our brain
and nervous system

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:11.456 align:middle line:84%
for more optimal functioning
in this experience of life.

