And this allows us to retain
the information better.

00:22:58.830 --> 00:23:01.760 align:middle line:10%
Now finally, there's also
higher range, the gamma range,

00:23:01.760 --> 00:23:05.210 align:middle line:10%
between 32 to 100 Hertz.

00:23:05.210 --> 00:23:07.460 align:middle line:10%
These are the highest
brainwave levels

00:23:07.460 --> 00:23:09.890 align:middle line:10%
that neuroscientists
have been able to detect

00:23:09.890 --> 00:23:11.780 align:middle line:10%
within our brains.

00:23:11.780 --> 00:23:16.400 align:middle line:84%
The main peak of the gamma waves
tends to be around 40 Hertz.

00:23:16.400 --> 00:23:19.490 align:middle line:84%
What's fascinating about
this 40 Hertz range

00:23:19.490 --> 00:23:22.700 align:middle line:84%
is that it has been associated
with peak creativity

00:23:22.700 --> 00:23:26.090 align:middle line:84%
and performance, as well
as visual processing

00:23:26.090 --> 00:23:30.200 align:middle line:84%
and what we call the unity
of conscious perception.

00:23:30.200 --> 00:23:33.680 align:middle line:84%
We reach these peak states
in times of elation,

00:23:33.680 --> 00:23:37.310 align:middle line:84%
mystical transcendence, and
when we're really in the zone.

