How do we intentionally
stimulate our brain

00:23:44.070 --> 00:23:46.380 align:middle line:84%
to create these
harmonized states

00:23:46.380 --> 00:23:50.670 align:middle line:84%
without having 20 years of
deep meditation practice?

00:23:50.670 --> 00:23:55.230 align:middle line:84%
The keys to doing so rests in
the principles of vibration,

00:23:55.230 --> 00:23:58.110 align:middle line:90%
resonance, and entrainment.

