00:25:49.490 --> 00:25:51.610 align:middle line:90%
for more optimal functioning.

00:25:51.610 --> 00:25:54.900 align:middle line:90%


00:25:54.900 --> 00:25:57.510 align:middle line:84%
Let's go back to
the corpus callosum.

00:25:57.510 --> 00:26:01.170 align:middle line:84%
What are the best methods for
creating greater connectivity

00:26:01.170 --> 00:26:04.950 align:middle line:84%
and balance here at
this part of the brain?

00:26:04.950 --> 00:26:09.660 align:middle line:84%
One simple exercise is
combining music and movement

00:26:09.660 --> 00:26:13.510 align:middle line:84%
that equally engages the
left and right sides.

00:26:13.510 --> 00:26:15.900 align:middle line:84%
It can be as simple as
putting on some good music

00:26:15.900 --> 00:26:18.810 align:middle line:84%
while going for a
brisk walk or run,

00:26:18.810 --> 00:26:22.800 align:middle line:84%
but be sure to have nothing in
your hands and swing your arms

00:26:22.800 --> 00:26:24.660 align:middle line:90%
as you walk or run.

00:26:24.660 --> 00:26:27.450 align:middle line:84%
This cross lateral
movement automatically

00:26:27.450 --> 00:26:30.750 align:middle line:84%
harmonizes the left
and right hemispheres.

00:26:30.750 --> 00:26:35.820 align:middle line:84%
Music also naturally engages
both hemispheres of the brain.

00:26:35.820 --> 00:26:40.590 align:middle line:84%
But the type of music we choose
to listen to is important.

00:26:40.590 --> 00:26:43.200 align:middle line:84%
When it comes to equally
harmonizing the brain,

00:26:43.200 --> 00:26:47.920 align:middle line:84%
selecting music without
lyrics or chants is important.

00:26:47.920 --> 00:26:50.940 align:middle line:84%
And the reason for that is
that lyrics put extra emphasis

00:26:50.940 --> 00:26:54.800 align:middle line:84%
into language centers of
the brain and the left side.

00:26:54.800 --> 00:26:57.730 align:middle line:84%
And in regular
situations, that's fine.

00:26:57.730 --> 00:27:00.990 align:middle line:84%
But when it comes to
achieving whole brain states,

00:27:00.990 --> 00:27:05.290 align:middle line:84%
it's best to use music
without language in it.

00:27:05.290 --> 00:27:07.590 align:middle line:84%
Another exercise that
we can do to balance

00:27:07.590 --> 00:27:12.570 align:middle line:84%
the hemispheres of the brain
is more of a visual process.

00:27:12.570 --> 00:27:15.780 align:middle line:84%
This one is an open
eye meditation,

00:27:15.780 --> 00:27:19.770 align:middle line:84%
focusing on a mandala with
balanced and symmetric

00:27:19.770 --> 00:27:21.210 align:middle line:90%
geometries.

00:27:21.210 --> 00:27:25.770 align:middle line:84%
When meditating on a mandala,
focus on the center point

00:27:25.770 --> 00:27:28.050 align:middle line:90%
or the balance points.

00:27:28.050 --> 00:27:33.240 align:middle line:84%
After connecting to it strongly
with the eyes open, eventually,

00:27:33.240 --> 00:27:38.670 align:middle line:84%
we then take it inward
and reconstruct it inside.

00:27:38.670 --> 00:27:40.740 align:middle line:84%
All of these
exercises will really

00:27:40.740 --> 00:27:44.760 align:middle line:84%
support this rewiring,
especially the prefrontals

00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:48.630 align:middle line:84%
and the corpus callosum, for a
more balanced and whole brain

00:27:48.630 --> 00:27:51.260 align:middle line:90%
state.

00:27:51.260 --> 00:27:54.860 align:middle line:84%
As we build a stronger
connection between the mind

00:27:54.860 --> 00:27:58.580 align:middle line:84%
and the brain, and as we
balance the two hemispheres

00:27:58.580 --> 00:28:03.020 align:middle line:84%
for optimal functioning,
we gain more authority

00:28:03.020 --> 00:28:06.290 align:middle line:90%
over our brain and body system.

00:28:06.290 --> 00:28:09.530 align:middle line:84%
And with this, we then
have greater ability

00:28:09.530 --> 00:28:13.790 align:middle line:84%
to master ourselves and
this vehicle of the body.

00:28:13.790 --> 00:28:16.070 align:middle line:84%
Mastering our
thoughts and emotions

00:28:16.070 --> 00:28:19.310 align:middle line:84%
is also essential
if we want to step

00:28:19.310 --> 00:28:22.100 align:middle line:84%
into our next phase
of human evolution

00:28:22.100 --> 00:28:26.390 align:middle line:84%
and become more fully
realized beings.

